{"tid":1373104,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我大陸朋友話公了唔到咪私了，班狗又無可能唔出狗竇","createTime":"2019-07-27T14:35:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T10:53:14.000Z","uid":33789,"like":248,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"2fcc43c05b888e03dccec5056da5bad631b5c264","tid":1373104,"uid":33789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T14:35:57.000Z","msg":"我朋友就住村既<br />\n成日見到班流浪狗出黎亂咬人，班狗隻隻都無狗牌又隻隻都畜生樣，正常人真係分唔到邊隻打邊隻，村公所又唔理，話班狗都係做緊天性會做既野，叫居民唔好出街<br />\n結果班村民比班狗咬左十幾次之後終於忍唔住決定反擊，點反擊呢，就係班狗每次咬完人隔一陣就扮自己係正常狗咁兩三隻返屋企<br />\n佢地就決定十幾個人出動跟蹤啲狗，一到啲隱蔽位就十幾個一齊圍隻流浪狗，然後割頸放血，最後煮比村民大家happy share，啲狗死既死，驚既驚<br />\n最後我朋友條村就無晒啲會亂咬人既流浪狗，村民過著幸福既生活<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c72e7c98fb58ee12a7ebb2e239b0d163e892eea6","tid":1373104,"uid":33789,"like":43,"dislike":1,"score":42,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T14:36:38.000Z","msg":"但殺狗真係好暴力血腥<br />\n大家聽下好啦呢個故事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"695aec102b34a2eb4a448f857a9476c17a088461","tid":1373104,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T14:36:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69344f20cd9c763f04059dd5c015b721f9ef7b5d","tid":1373104,"uid":173849,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T14:38:20.000Z","msg":"自動當選選區剩下28個，元朗天水圍區佔13<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1372729\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1372729</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"da01692829320196149f0dba16f755c822f19f15","tid":1373104,"uid":33789,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T14:38:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好人一世平安"},{"pid":"aa08b247976c647b47cf95475b28f6380c71e7dc","tid":1373104,"uid":33789,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T14:41:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"